$ WAVEWATCH III initial-conditions preprocessor.
$
$ Type 5 = JONSWAP-like seed driven by local wind. Avoids the silent-spectrum
$ problem (no growth without seed); equivalent to Ripple's `set!(model, N=1e-6)`
$ but matched to the wind speed.
$
$ ITYPE
   5
$
$ For ITYPE=5: alpha, fp, wind direction, sigma_A, sigma_B, gamma
$ Pierson-Moskowitz f_p estimate for U=17 m/s: f_p ≈ 0.13 g/U10 ≈ 0.075 Hz
   0.005  0.075  90.   0.07  0.09  3.3
$
$ End.
